name: DwnSinSqUp
description:
I created this piece to experiment creating visuals to visualize sounds.
The audio was created with Ableton using four wavetable devices. 
Three of the wavetables are controlled by LFOs: one down sawtooth wave, one up sawtooth wave and one square wave. 
There's an auto pan controlled by a sine wave.. all four together is where the name of this piece comes from.
Each wave has been visualized within the piece.
